Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Special relationship especially warm
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03zjl5q
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 25 Jul 1976
US-UK special relationship especially warm this summer. UK tourism figures boom. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.